data.name: description3.Text
data.value: Bask in the golden gleam of our radiant Sunlit Cascade mini bouquet. Crowned with a fresh sunflower, this effervescent arrangement features a medley of lush foliage and aster blooms - perfect for adding a touch of brightness and magic to that special someone's day!

data.name: description.Text
data.value: Bring a sun-filled smile to their face and set their heart aflutter with our incredibly adorable Sunlight Posy flower bouquet. Topped with radiant yellow gerberas and accompanied by a mix of lush foliage, this lively mini bouquet is guaranteed to infuse their day with rays of happiness and add an extra bounce in their step.

data.name: description2.Text
data.value: Surprise that special someone, with the refined beauty of our Ivory Elegance flower bouquet, featuring a graceful arrangement of pristine white carnations with bursts of vibrant red berries, thoughtfully arranged amid sprays of lush foliage. Encapsulating a sense of wonderful sophistication, this bouquetserves as a perfect expression of your admiration, best wishes and love.

data.name: Label9.Text
data.value: Discover Enchanted Bloom's elegant Flower Bouquet Collection, featuring handcrafted arrangements for every occasion. With tulips, roses, sunflowers, and more, our vibrant bouquets are perfect for expressing love and appreciation. Choose Flower Chimp for unforgettable memories and heartwarming smiles.

data.name: description4.Text
data.value: Gentle caresses of pastel pink, orange & purple hues, medleyed together to bring you our whimsical Astraea flower bouquet. Featuring a miscellany of roses, tulips & berries - this arrangement makes the perfect pick for the most magical celebrations that life sends your way.
